OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer faced MPs for his
OL,7,Ffinal Prime Minister's Questions on
OL,8,FWednesday, with many tributes, a
OL,9,Flittering of football jokes and tears
OL,10,Fby the end.
OL,12,FIt comes as Andy Burnham takes over as
OL,13,FLabour leader on Friday and
OL,14,Fsubsequently as prime minister on
OL,15,FMonday.
OL,17,FThe questions opened with a focus on
OL,18,Ftributes for former MP Ann Widdecombe,
OL,19,Fwho was allegedly murdered on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
