OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784121522
OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FStarmer said "we must do more to
OL,7,Fdefend our democracy", as well as
OL,8,Fsuggesting a shield be added to the
OL,9,Fcommons in honour of Widdecombe,
OL,10,Fsimilar to that of murdered MP's Jo
OL,11,FCox and David Amess.
OL,13,FOpposition leader Kemi Badenoch paid
OL,14,Ftribute to the former Conservative
OL,15,Fminister, calling Widdecombe "a woman
OL,16,Fof high principle, profound beliefs,
OL,17,Fwith a wicked sense of humour".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
