OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe mood was mixed as MPs then focused
OL,12,Fon the World Cup and made lighthearted
OL,13,Fjokes ahead of the prime minister's
OL,14,Fexit.
OL,16,FA question from Conservative MP Graham
OL,17,FStuart compared the outgoing PM to
OL,18,Ffootball superstar Jude Bellingham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784121522
OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FStuart said the PM had played the role
OL,7,Fof the England No 10 by "scoring the
OL,8,Fwinning goal and leading our team to
OL,9,Fvictory" but went on to compare the
OL,10,Fsport with politics, calling it "a
OL,11,Fruthless game".
OL,13,FHe joked that the PM has "been handed
OL,14,Fa red card by the 400 dodgy referees"
OL,15,Fand asked what Starmer's advice would
OL,16,Fbe to Burnham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784121522
OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FStarmer replied that it is likely "the
OL,7,Ffirst and sadly probably the last
OL,8,Ftime" he will be compared to the
OL,9,Ffootball star and said "he won't give
OL,10,Fadvice" but instead gives his
OL,11,F"wholehearted support".
OL,13,FThe PM, a keen football fan, went on
OL,14,Fto focus on England's semi-final match
OL,15,Fand said: "I don't care what the score
OL,16,Fis tonight, as long as we win."
OL,18,FIf England head to the final on
OL,19,FSunday, Starmer will attend, in what
OL,20,Fwould be his final act as prime
OL,21,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
