OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784121522
OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FStarmer was keen to defend his record
OL,7,Fand Badenoch paid tribute to his
OL,8,Fsuccesses throughout her remarks,
OL,9,Fnoting particularly his work with
OL,10,FUkraine saying it was the "one thing I
OL,11,Fdid admire".
OL,13,FThis was the PM's invitation to
OL,14,FUkrainian president Volodymyr
OL,15,FZelenskyy to visit Downing Street
OL,16,Fafter Trump "evicted" him from the
OL,17,FWhite House, Starmer said "we have
OL,18,Fstood united on Ukraine in this House".
OL,20,FIn another mood switch, the session
OL,21,Fended in tears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
