OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FLabour MP Carolyn Harris cried through
OL,7,Fthe final question to her "dear
OL,8,Ffriend" saying "we've seen his decency
OL,9,Fand courage shine through" and wishing
OL,10,Fhim and his family well.
OL,12,FStarmer continued this tribute to his
OL,13,Fwife and children, who were watching
OL,14,Fin the gallery simply telling them "I
OL,15,Flove you" following a stream of thanks
OL,16,Ffor his colleagues across the Commons,
OL,17,Fcivil servants and his political team.
OL,19,FSitting behind him, Chancellor Rachel
OL,20,FReeves was crying as Starmer said his
OL,21,Ffinal goodbye.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
