OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784121522
OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FHe credited "all across the country
OL,7,Fwho struggle to be seen or heard" as
OL,8,Fhis reason for coming in to politics,
OL,9,Fbut calling it "the end of my
OL,10,Fpolitical journey".
OL,12,FBefore appearing in parliament,
OL,13,FStarmer invited people whose "lives
OL,14,Fhave been improved as a result of
OL,15,Fdecisions made by this government",
OL,16,Fkeen to highlight the work that he had
OL,17,Fdone during his time in No 10 before
OL,18,Fhis exit on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
