OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FThese guests were in the gallery to
OL,7,Fwatch his final grilling and Starmer
OL,8,Fmade many references to their life
OL,9,Fstories and how his government has
OL,10,Fhelped them.
OL,12,FStarmer noted Pooja Kanda, who's son
OL,13,FRonan was murdered by a teenager who
OL,14,Fbough a ninja sword online and the
OL,15,Fgovernment has since passed Ronan's
OL,16,FLaw, outlawing the manufacture,
OL,17,Fsupply, sale and possession of ninja
OL,18,Fswords.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784121522
OL,3,CTears, jokes and tributes: Starmer's
OL,4,Cfinal PMQs
OL,6,FHe also praised a breast cancer
OL,7,Fadvocate, a mother who is fighting for
OL,8,Fonline safety measures and campaigner
OL,9,Ffor cost of living support.
OL,11,FBurnham, who will become Labour leader
OL,12,Fon Friday and then prime minister on
OL,13,FMonday, was not in the Commons,
OL,14,Fdespite many references to the future
OL,15,Fgovernment.
OL,17,FBurnham made his first appearance in
OL,18,Fthe chamber on Tuesday evening,
OL,19,Fdelivering his maiden speech during
OL,20,Fthe debate on the Hillsborough Law,
OL,21,Fwhich is due to pass as law imminently.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
